Confusion vs. Complexity.#Learn the difference between confusion and complexity.
Complexity is a status of a thing. Things can be complex. Confusion is a mental state. It is inside of you, a reflection of your relationship to the software.
When you are confused, stop and figure out what it is that is confusing you. &ldquo;Why did this person in this video tutorial choose to do it this way?&rdquo;
